  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Trilateral Research Chairs (2018-2022)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A 3-5 year trilateral research partnership between a university in the UK, SA and any other African country. This supports the aims of the SARChI initiative (South African Research Chairs) to enable research excellence. The call attracts leading scientists</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Each chair will support research excellence acrosss the UK-SA and Africa through joint research led by 3 leading and established researchers/ research chairs and capacity building for early career researchers ( mentorship/ mobility, Masters and PhD scholarships)</narrative>
  </description>
